OL,7,FFarming is an industry harking back
OL,8,Fgenerations - in fact is believed to
OL,9,Fhave started in Ireland more than
OL,10,F6,000 years ago.
OL,12,FHowever, it's an industry that's
OL,13,Fpresently facing a number of issues.
OL,15,FA second consecutive wet summer, a
OL,16,Fcontinuous battle against the effects
OL,17,Fof inflation and rising costs relating
OL,18,Fto production are hitting farmers'
OL,19,Fpockets and having an effect on their
OL,20,Fmental health.
