OL,7,FAdd to that, the number of local
OL,8,Fworking farms in Northern Ireland has
OL,9,Fdecreased by around a third since
OL,10,F1981, according to a report released
OL,11,Fearlier this year meaning more demand
OL,12,Fon those that have survived. 20,077
OL,13,Fdown from 40,700.
OL,15,FWallace Gregg owns a dairy farm in
OL,16,FCloughmills, Co Antrim.
OL,18,FHe told UTV that he is 'milking more
OL,19,Fcows than ever' and finds himself no
OL,20,Fbetter off financially than his father
OL,21,Fwas.
