OL,7,F"We just seem to have to work harder
OL,8,Fto stand still and unfortunately that
OL,9,Fjust cost pressures," he said.
OL,11,FFarming on Life Support was produced
OL,12,Fby Professor Paul Gosling back in May.
OL,14,FIt revealed that farming accounts for
OL,15,F1.6% of the overall economy in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,18,FYoung farmers like Clodagh Lavery,
OL,19,Fwant to contribute to that and help it
OL,20,Fgrow even further.
